3. **`org.jsoup.nodes.Attributes:put`** - This method adds attributes to the collection and may be relevant if there are issues with how attributes are being managed.
4. **`org.jsoup.nodes.Attributes:iterator`** - This method provides an iterator for the attributes and could be involved in the concurrent modification issue.
5. **`org.jsoup.nodes.Attributes:remove`** - This method is used to remove an attribute from the collection and may also be relevant to the issue.
